overview.zh: PAW is a digital currency. It uses a new form of distribution model that no longer excludes people because of a lack of technical knowledge or resources. Rewards are being given out similar to mining in 10 minutes cycles. It's an animal themed currency that includes every kind of animal person and is building on a efficient technology that allows for near instant settlements with zero transaction fees.
